@title{Metadata}

@p{There are several metadata can be set to a card, list as below:}
@ol{
  @li{@code["@taxon{...}"] it accepts a text}
  @li{@code["@title{...}"] it accepts a list of forms}
  @li{@code["@author{...}"] it only accepts a card address}
  @li{@code["@author/literal{...}"] it accepts a text}
  @li{@code["@date{...}"] it accepts a text, but I suggest in @code{yyyy/mm/dd} format}
}
